

Commands Package Termux
=======================

      Commands                Description
      --------                -----------
      ?                       help menu
      ls		      Show all files
      exit		      exit Exit from the tool
      show		      Show what's inside the file
      clear		      Cleaning the terminal screen 
      banner		      Refresh and logo change
      pkg_termux              Create a file with commands
      update_termux           Update Termux Package tools
      upgrade_termux          Update and upgrade tools


